2





904 Rainforest PkwyColumbia, MO 65202


        (888) 438-2427
    






I loved having Charter internet. They don't have a data cap like all the other companies seem to now (when did they all develop the delusion that they are cell phone companies instead of wired internet companies??)

I never had any problems with the modem or the internet service from Charter (in stark contrast to when I had Centurylink at the same address - that was an absolute nightmare and I vehemently recommend to anyone who is looking for internet service Do Not Get Centurylink!). 

My only complaint about Charter is that they don't offer service in the Columbia, Mo city limits so I lost them when I moved. :(

Charter, if you're reading this, know that if you expand into the city limits you will have at least one guaranteed customer who will sing your praises to all the neighbors.







"Just works". Can't say that about the other cable provider in town. Consistent downloads speeds above 60 Mbps.







            Charter Communications
        





