                and number of channels may vary; Not all channels available in HD; HD channels are
                included at no additional cost; TV equipment required & is extra.
ON DEMAND: On Demand programming varies by level of service; pricing, ratings
                & scheduling are subject to change; TV equipment required & is extra.
3D: 3D viewing requires 3D TV, glasses & compatible set top box; programming
                varies by level of service.
DOLBY DIGITAL 5.1 SURROUND SOUND: Dolby is a registered trademark of Dolby
                Laboratories.
PAY-PER-VIEW: PPV programming, pricing, ratings & scheduling are subject
                to change.
