CHARTER SPECTRUM INTERNET™

SPEEDS: Available Internet speeds may vary by address; small percent of customers
                will receive lower than advertised speeds. **Speeds compared to 3Mbps DSL.
ONLINE PHONE MANAGER: Must subscribe to Charter Internet and Phone &
                have a charter.com or 
                    Charter.net account log in to access & use Phone Online Manager service.
INTERNET MODEM: Lease of Internet modem included.
STREAMING CONTENT: Must subscribe to corresponding level of service to receive
                their online service and apps; trademarks belong to their respective owners.
CHARTER SECURITY SUITE®: Charter does not guarantee data will be secure.
CHARTER WIFI®: Charter Internet required. Equipment, activation and installation
                fees apply.

